creator: LionTech Solutions Pvt. Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
All-In-One agriculture and Farm input Shop

Agrowala Application is an All In One Store for farmers where they can buy any original items of agriculture and farm inputs. Farmers can buy Seeds, Pesticides, Fertilizers, Spray Pumps, Submersible Pumps, Farm Equipment like Seeds drill machines, Rotavator, tractors etc., other farm usage items like Ferro man traps, tarpaulin, mulching sheets etc.

Farmers get a complete guideline on all the diseases and pests of all the crops.
They can get crop solutions recommended by experts and they can share this information with other farmers as well.
Return policy on certain items as per seller’s policy.
Products sold are of top brands only.
Products sold are all verified before getting delivered.
Wide ranges of products are sold for each category.
Farmers can purchase with a payment option of Cash on Delivery.
Items are delivered at their home.
The application is presently available in Gujarati and English language.
The Application is very easy to use and even a new android user can easily place an order.
Farmers get the coupon codes or discount offers on deals.
Farmers can save time and fuel by ordering an item while sitting at their home.
Farmers get articles and news feed related to agriculture in their application.
Any Android user can use this application.
